<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: connection_zone_based_fabrication_joint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Fabrication_joint_mim.connection_zone_based_fabrication_joint">
<p>
	A <b>connection_zone_based_fabrication_joint</b> is a type of 
	<express_ref linkend="Fabrication_joint:mim:Fabrication_joint_mim.fabrication_joint"/> 
	that implements the ARM concept of 
	<express_ref linkend="Fabrication_joint:arm:Fabrication_joint_arm.Connection_zone_based_fabrication_joint"/>.
	A <b>connection_zone_based_fabrication_joint</b> includes the
	identification of the connection zones that are to be mated in addition to the specific
	features that are to be mated. 
</p>
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: fabrication_joint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Fabrication_joint_mim.fabrication_joint">
<p>

A <b>fabrication_joint</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="Component_feature:mim:Component_feature_mim.component_feature_joint"/> that implements the ARM concept
of  <express_ref linkend="Fabrication_joint:arm:Fabrication_joint_arm.Fabrication_joint"/>.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: fabrication_joint.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Fabrication_joint_mim.fabrication_joint.wr:WR1">
The <b>fabrication_joint</b> shall relate to either at most one land or to at most one  <express_ref linkend="Physical_unit_design_view:mim:Physical_unit_design_view_mim.component_definition"/> that has a description of 'stratum feature template component', to specify the 'auxiliary joint material'.
</ext_description>

